title: United States of Tara
description: Tara, a suburban wife and mother, suffers from Dissociative Identity Disorder. There's never a dull moment, as her various personalities may appear on any given day...

title: American Housewife
description: Katie Mixon is many things, a housewife is just one. She's trying to raise a family, and stay true to herself among the perfect people of Conneticut.
